WEBVTT

00:00:00.010 --> 00:00:25.890
Subtitle Provide by dramacool.asia Translator [Admin.@YNG]

00:00:29.820 --> 00:00:34.860
[Echoes of the Self]

00:00:38.380 --> 00:00:39.180
How dare you!

00:00:39.670 --> 00:00:41.150
How dare you defy me!

00:00:49.450 --> 00:00:50.930
Zhou Ruoxi?

00:00:54.590 --> 00:00:55.390
This...

00:00:56.100 --> 00:00:56.900
Oh no!

00:00:57.180 --> 00:00:57.980
Bad news!

00:00:58.560 --> 00:01:00.290
The one who went to Yuzhou is...

00:01:01.970 --> 00:01:03.780
Ask someone to go to Yuzhou immediately.

00:01:03.780 --> 00:01:05.340
Don't let her return alive!

00:01:05.370 --> 00:01:06.010
Yes.

00:01:06.130 --> 00:01:06.730
Go!

00:01:25.630 --> 00:01:26.550
I knew we would

00:01:26.680 --> 00:01:29.280
find unimpeded access
through this entrance.

00:01:30.730 --> 00:01:33.130
How dare you let me
crawl through a dog hole!

00:01:34.740 --> 00:01:35.940
And you're laughing?

00:01:50.020 --> 00:01:51.420
Let's go, Your Highness.

00:02:08.850 --> 00:02:10.590
The clue Your Highness mentioned

00:02:10.590 --> 00:02:11.750
is in the kitchen?

00:02:17.130 --> 00:02:18.360
[Wang's Mansion]

00:02:18.360 --> 00:02:19.000
Hurry up!

00:02:19.000 --> 00:02:21.800
In my previous life, the Wang family
was raided due to loan sharking.

00:02:21.800 --> 00:02:25.400
-Record every item clearly.
-The money was found in the cellar.

00:02:38.750 --> 00:02:39.610
Your Highness.

00:03:20.700 --> 00:03:21.960
How could this happen?

00:03:22.840 --> 00:03:24.440
It seems we arrived too late.

00:03:29.560 --> 00:03:30.420
Your Highness.

00:03:30.700 --> 00:03:31.670
Someone's coming.

00:03:31.670 --> 00:03:32.890
If there is any chance later,

00:03:32.890 --> 00:03:33.690
you go first.

00:03:43.790 --> 00:03:45.530
[Memorial Tablet of Ancestor Zhou Wenbin]

00:03:58.790 --> 00:04:00.050
What are you doing?

00:04:00.730 --> 00:04:03.900
[Memorial Tablet of Ancestor Zhou Wenbin]

00:04:07.790 --> 00:04:08.510
Tell me!

00:04:08.540 --> 00:04:10.800
Why are you impersonating the princess?

00:04:11.030 --> 00:04:12.650
What scheme are you

00:04:12.860 --> 00:04:14.720
and Princess of Daqing plotting?

00:04:15.110 --> 00:04:17.279
It has nothing to do with Her Highness.

00:04:18.010 --> 00:04:19.810
I just wanted to use her identity

00:04:20.040 --> 00:04:21.440
to avenge my mother.

00:04:25.140 --> 00:04:27.440
I don't think you are that smart

00:04:27.470 --> 00:04:28.790
and brave.

00:04:29.110 --> 00:04:29.910
Tell me!

00:04:30.770 --> 00:04:32.530
When did you collude

00:04:32.550 --> 00:04:33.810
and what are you after?

00:04:35.810 --> 00:04:37.470
Refused to say anything, huh?

00:04:37.930 --> 00:04:38.490
Hmph!

00:04:38.770 --> 00:04:39.610
Fine.

00:04:40.600 --> 00:04:42.420
Then you'll have no chance to explain.

00:04:42.420 --> 00:04:44.040
After I settle everything,

00:04:44.760 --> 00:04:47.990
I will kill you.

00:04:47.990 --> 00:04:51.510
[Memorial Tablet of Ancestor Zhou Wenbin]

00:05:01.000 --> 00:05:01.800
Today,

00:05:03.190 --> 00:05:04.620
I will stand by you
through thick and thin.

00:05:04.620 --> 00:05:05.660
Attack!

00:05:54.480 --> 00:05:55.360
Watch out!

00:06:41.150 --> 00:06:42.390
Your Highness,

00:06:43.560 --> 00:06:44.880
are you alright?

00:06:47.080 --> 00:06:48.000
I'm fine.

00:08:41.950 --> 00:08:43.549
Could the person in my dreams

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:44.880
be her?

00:08:59.450 --> 00:09:00.820
Have we met before?

00:09:06.760 --> 00:09:07.560
No.

00:09:13.360 --> 00:09:14.280
Then, why

00:09:16.050 --> 00:09:18.180
do I always feel so familiar with you?

00:09:20.340 --> 00:09:22.600
Your Highness, please behave yourself.

00:09:42.330 --> 00:09:44.590
I came to Yunrui for a marriage alliance.

00:09:47.610 --> 00:09:49.810
Since you came for a marriage alliance,

00:09:51.960 --> 00:09:53.880
why don't you marry me?

00:10:00.360 --> 00:10:02.410
I've caused you trouble.

00:10:02.800 --> 00:10:04.810
If there's another life,

00:10:08.580 --> 00:10:09.780
I wish you would never

00:10:10.930 --> 00:10:13.420
meet me.

00:10:14.410 --> 00:10:17.010
I don't want to have any relationship
with you.

00:10:17.460 --> 00:10:19.930
Then, why did you ask me to come to Yuzhou

00:10:20.230 --> 00:10:22.160
and investigate the case with you?

00:10:25.820 --> 00:10:26.950
Because I trust you.

00:10:32.720 --> 00:10:34.180
I truly don't understand.

00:10:37.460 --> 00:10:38.620
I can't explain it

00:10:40.530 --> 00:10:41.610
to you.

00:10:44.700 --> 00:10:46.230
Please don't ask anymore.

00:11:05.760 --> 00:11:07.950
Tomorrow I'll bring some people
to investigate the Wang family.

00:11:07.950 --> 00:11:08.830
I'll say

00:11:09.330 --> 00:11:12.590
we have found the ledger of
their loan-sharking business.

00:11:28.950 --> 00:11:30.090
Yan.

00:11:34.580 --> 00:11:35.810
I'm sorry.

00:11:49.780 --> 00:11:50.630
Your Highness,

00:11:50.630 --> 00:11:51.510
you're hurt!

00:11:51.810 --> 00:11:52.790
I'll get a doctor.

00:11:52.790 --> 00:11:53.430
No need.

00:11:55.920 --> 00:11:57.640
Deliver a message to my brother first.

00:11:57.640 --> 00:11:59.520
Ask him to come here immediately
with his men.

00:11:59.520 --> 00:12:00.320
Something big

00:12:01.740 --> 00:12:03.340
is about to happen in Yuzhou.

00:12:05.950 --> 00:12:07.050
The Wang family in Yuzhou

00:12:07.050 --> 00:12:08.010
secretly engaged in loan sharking

00:12:08.010 --> 00:12:08.470
[Wang's Mansion]

00:12:08.470 --> 00:12:09.560
and attempted to assassinate
the royal family members.

00:12:09.560 --> 00:12:10.850
They have committed heinous crimes.

00:12:10.850 --> 00:12:14.380
All members of the Wang family
will be detained awaiting trial.

00:12:15.100 --> 00:12:15.940
Hurry up!

00:12:26.250 --> 00:12:27.590
We've settled everything.

00:12:27.590 --> 00:12:28.630
Unfortunately,

00:12:28.650 --> 00:12:30.010
those two escaped.

00:12:30.060 --> 00:12:33.390
Why did Prince Yan go to such lengths
to raid the Wang family?

00:12:34.100 --> 00:12:35.130
Where is the ledger?

00:12:35.130 --> 00:12:35.860
Here you are.

00:12:40.930 --> 00:12:42.190
How could this happen?

00:12:42.640 --> 00:12:44.250
Just as Your Highness predicted,

00:12:44.250 --> 00:12:45.990
evil men would
deliver the ledger themselves.

00:12:45.990 --> 00:12:47.740
I can't let the ledger fall into
anyone else's hands.

00:12:47.740 --> 00:12:48.500
Attack!

00:12:57.320 --> 00:12:57.960
Thirteen!

00:12:59.120 --> 00:12:59.840
Brother.

00:13:02.200 --> 00:13:02.920
Next time

00:13:03.240 --> 00:13:04.760
if you need help,

00:13:04.790 --> 00:13:06.790
you should tell me about it earlier.

00:13:07.610 --> 00:13:09.340
I don't want to see your corpse.

00:13:10.280 --> 00:13:11.160
You came

00:13:11.180 --> 00:13:12.020
just in time.

00:13:21.800 --> 00:13:24.380
I kept indulging her
to make her become more and more greedy

00:13:24.380 --> 00:13:26.140
for today.

00:13:27.810 --> 00:13:29.360
You once said

00:13:30.170 --> 00:13:32.530
you wanted to be my blade.

00:13:34.140 --> 00:13:36.140
Now, all of this is

00:13:36.580 --> 00:13:38.820
your own fault.

00:13:45.150 --> 00:13:46.010
Your Highness,

00:13:46.350 --> 00:13:48.280
this is the Crown Prince of Yunrui.

00:13:52.820 --> 00:13:54.080
The Princess of Daqing

00:13:54.300 --> 00:13:56.900
looks exactly like Miss Zhou Ruoxi.

00:14:00.630 --> 00:14:01.480
Don't move!

00:14:07.460 --> 00:14:08.050
Your Highness,

00:14:08.050 --> 00:14:09.110
here is the ledger.

00:14:10.550 --> 00:14:12.410
This is evidence
of the loan-sharking case.

00:14:12.410 --> 00:14:13.470
Please take a look.

00:14:18.860 --> 00:14:20.990
Is Xi in danger?

00:14:24.610 --> 00:14:25.470
Your Highness.

00:14:37.170 --> 00:14:38.800
What are you doing?

00:14:42.510 --> 00:14:43.900
The Wang family in Yuzhou

00:14:43.900 --> 00:14:45.370
secretly engaged in loan sharking.

00:14:45.370 --> 00:14:46.730
Madam Wang is dead.

00:14:47.280 --> 00:14:49.910
Now her daughter, Zhou Ruoxi,

00:14:50.220 --> 00:14:52.550
has been overwhelmed
with longing for her mother

00:14:52.550 --> 00:14:55.080
and set herself on fire
in the ancestral hall.

00:15:01.200 --> 00:15:01.960
If you kill me,

00:15:01.960 --> 00:15:03.760
Princess Fu Wei
won't let you go.

00:15:05.850 --> 00:15:08.130
You two switched identities

00:15:08.880 --> 00:15:11.760
to investigate the mastermind
behind the loan-sharking case.

00:15:11.760 --> 00:15:15.020
Fu Wei has already been captured by
my men in Yuzhou.

00:15:15.240 --> 00:15:17.100
I think she might have died now.

00:15:17.740 --> 00:15:19.220
Neither you nor Fu Wei

00:15:19.340 --> 00:15:21.020
will make it out alive.

00:15:23.760 --> 00:15:25.280
From this day forward,

00:15:25.300 --> 00:15:27.180
no one can get in my way.

00:15:30.730 --> 00:15:32.130
Help!

00:15:32.160 --> 00:15:33.950
Help me!

00:15:36.220 --> 00:15:37.740
Help!

00:15:39.500 --> 00:15:41.090
Help!

00:15:41.710 --> 00:15:43.230
Help me!

00:15:47.340 --> 00:15:49.000
Fire! Fire!

00:15:49.030 --> 00:15:49.470
Hurry!

00:15:49.490 --> 00:15:50.750
Hurry! Hurry!

00:15:51.170 --> 00:15:52.290
Water!

00:15:52.320 --> 00:15:53.330
Here is water.

00:15:54.100 --> 00:15:56.020
Hurry up! This place! This place!

00:15:56.220 --> 00:15:57.860
Here is water!

00:15:58.010 --> 00:15:58.850
Hurry up!

00:15:58.880 --> 00:15:59.960
Here!

00:16:02.020 --> 00:16:02.930
What's happening?

00:16:02.930 --> 00:16:03.330
Ah!

00:16:03.350 --> 00:16:04.610
How could this happen?

00:16:04.840 --> 00:16:05.360
My Lord,

00:16:05.380 --> 00:16:06.260
we have no idea.

00:16:06.290 --> 00:16:07.510
The fire suddenly broke out.

00:16:07.510 --> 00:16:08.360
Put out the fire quickly!

00:16:08.360 --> 00:16:09.760
Put out the fire quickly!

00:16:12.110 --> 00:16:13.730
Hurry and put out the fire!

00:16:17.490 --> 00:16:18.360
Hurry! Hurry up!

00:16:18.360 --> 00:16:19.060
This place!

00:16:19.090 --> 00:16:20.130
Xi!

00:16:23.160 --> 00:16:23.960
How could...

00:16:24.400 --> 00:16:24.840
Xi!

00:16:24.840 --> 00:16:25.600
Let me do it.

00:16:28.440 --> 00:16:29.200
This place!

00:16:30.330 --> 00:16:31.230
Here!

00:16:37.280 --> 00:16:38.040
Hurry!

00:16:38.380 --> 00:16:39.480
Here is water!

00:16:42.560 --> 00:16:43.320
Xi!

00:16:43.510 --> 00:16:44.270
Miss Ruoxi,

00:16:44.290 --> 00:16:45.030
it's too dangerous inside.

00:16:45.030 --> 00:16:45.540
You can't go in!

00:16:45.540 --> 00:16:46.250
Get out of my way!

00:16:46.250 --> 00:16:46.770
Move!

00:16:46.790 --> 00:16:47.500
It's too dangerous!

00:16:47.500 --> 00:16:48.980
I am Princess Fu Wei!

00:16:49.000 --> 00:16:49.800
Move aside!

00:16:53.360 --> 00:16:54.200
Xi!

00:17:00.960 --> 00:17:01.850
Xi!

00:17:02.750 --> 00:17:03.630
Xi!

00:17:04.050 --> 00:17:05.000
Xi,

00:17:05.109 --> 00:17:06.040
are you alright?

00:17:11.960 --> 00:17:12.700
How...

00:17:12.940 --> 00:17:14.740
How can there be two Xi?

00:17:16.569 --> 00:17:17.490
Madam Cui,

00:17:18.859 --> 00:17:19.940
I will

00:17:20.990 --> 00:17:23.130
let you pay the price.